# MAINFRAME DISCOVERY PLATFORM IMPLEMENTATION GUIDE

# Objective

Build a reusable Mainframe Discovery Platform capable of analyzing large enterprise mainframe repositories containing:

* COBOL
* JCL
* Copybooks
* DB2
* CICS
* Control-M/Scheduler artifacts

The platform should support:

* Repository discovery
* Dependency analysis
* Root program discovery
* Data lineage
* Impact analysis
* Business rule extraction
* Natural language Q&A
* Future modernization

