# COPILOT USAGE RULE

Always use this sequence:

1. Ask for Architecture
2. Ask for Review
3. Ask for Improvements
4. Ask for Implementation
5. Ask for Tests
6. Ask for Code Review
7. Ask for Refactoring

Never start with:

"Write the code"

Always start with:

"Design the architecture"

This single habit will dramatically improve Copilot output quality.
